EDragon, an online RPG free to play game on http://www.lekool.com

A mythical world of skill, might and magic!
The adventure of a Knight, Assassin, Elf, Dwarf or a Barbarian in an interactive world of fantasy.

Play at http://edragon.lekool.com,
facebook fan page: http://www.facebook.com/pages/EDragon/138353566238769?ref=ts

Music: Kevin MacLeod at Incompetech.com

Video by Cromar and LeKoOl

Tell us what you think in the comments below.

If you like this video, click "Like" and Subscribe to our channel to get more!
